ingredients:
- steaks
- butters
- garlics
- skillets

howto:
1. heat up skillet
2. when skillet is hot add some butter and let it melt
3. place steak onto skillet
4. do not play with your meat!
5. flip at around two minutes
6. do not play with your meat!
7. flip again after two minutes
8. add crushed garlics and melted butter to the pan
9. allow meats to rest for a few mins
10. add potatoes to plate and perhaps asparaguses that magically cooked themselves because I clearly forgot to mention them in the ingredients list.